00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.895
In this lesson, we will learn how to integrate Google Search Console with their website.

00:00:05.895 --> 00:00:08.985
So what is Google Search Console?

00:00:08.985 --> 00:00:14.070
Well, Google Search Console is a free platform for anyone with a website to

00:00:14.070 --> 00:00:19.825
monitor how Google views their website and optimize the organic presence.

00:00:19.825 --> 00:00:24.755
This includes viewing the referring domains, rich search results,

00:00:24.755 --> 00:00:29.090
highest traffic search queries and pages, submitting the sitemap,

00:00:29.090 --> 00:00:33.920
requesting for indexing and getting to know the headers on the pages.

00:00:33.920 --> 00:00:38.945
It is an excellent platform to analyze the organic data of the website.

00:00:38.945 --> 00:00:41.870
So to integrate Google Search Console,

00:00:41.870 --> 00:00:46.160
make a search for Google search console and click on start.

00:00:46.160 --> 00:00:49.175
Now login with the same Google account as

00:00:49.175 --> 00:00:52.520
you have used for Google Tag Manager and Google Analytics.

00:00:52.520 --> 00:00:55.355
Now, you need to select the property type,

00:00:55.355 --> 00:01:01.380
enter the URL of the website in the URL prefix option and click on Continue.

00:01:01.960 --> 00:01:08.525
They had said your website will be auto verified using the Google Tag Manager

00:01:08.525 --> 00:01:10.760
because you have already integrated

00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:15.500
Google Tag Manager on the website with the same Google account.

00:01:15.500 --> 00:01:21.485
If due to some reasons you are unable to verify the property using Google Tag Manager,

00:01:21.485 --> 00:01:24.095
then you can follow the secondary method.

00:01:24.095 --> 00:01:26.870
Go to the settings in Search Console,

00:01:26.870 --> 00:01:29.330
click on ownership verification,

00:01:29.330 --> 00:01:31.325
click on the HTML tag,

00:01:31.325 --> 00:01:35.915
copy the tag, and paste this in the Yoast SEO plug-in.

00:01:35.915 --> 00:01:39.740
Well, Yoast SEO plugin is essential to optimize

00:01:39.740 --> 00:01:44.030
their website for on-page SEO and you are definitely going to use it.

00:01:44.030 --> 00:01:47.614
Then go to the Yoast SEO genitals attains,

00:01:47.614 --> 00:01:49.400
click on Webmaster Tools,

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:53.960
paste a verification code here and click on save changes.

00:01:53.960 --> 00:01:58.715
Now click on Verify and the property will be verified.

00:01:58.715 --> 00:02:05.750
So start using the Search Console and analyze the different data and reports available.

00:02:05.750 --> 00:02:08.970
We will continue in the next video.
